PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1992-1925, as amended by P.C. 1992-2571, which postpones the coming into force of those provisions (subsections 19(3) and (4)) concerning the conditions for obtaining a Firearms Acquisition Certificate, from July 1, 1993 to January 1, 1994.
